          alt="Horizontal flow diagram: Market Messaging → Conversion Path → Lead Flow → CRM Structure → Handoff Rules → Revenue Visibility → Adoption. Caption: Revenue architecture connects Japan-facing GTM strategy with the operating system needed to execute it."
          width="760"
